{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_FireCrossbowPL2}}
'''A_FireCrossbowPL2'''<br>
(''no parameter'')<br>

Shoots three {{Class|CrossbowFX2}} as main projectiles (one straight ahead and the two others deviating from the first by an angle of 4.5° on either side) and two {{Class|CrossbowFX3}} that deviate from the central projectile by an angle of 9°, one of the right, the other on the left.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|CrossbowPowered}} and derived classes.

